Create/Modify a user:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p user -i
Delete the default raspberry user:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p del_stduser -i
Create SSH keypair for a user:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p sshkey -i
Enable/Disable SSH:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p ssh -i
Change the system hostname:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p host -i
Change the system timezone:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p tzone -i
Change the system locales:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p locale -i
Change the system audio channel:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p audio -i
Change the keyboard layout:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p keyb -i
Change the default boot environment:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p bootenv -i
Change the GPU-reserved memory:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p memsplit -i
Change wether to wait for network on boot:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p netwait -i
Change the display overscan:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p overscan -i
Change all settings:\"${PH_SUDO}\" confoper_ph.sh -p all -i
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
System:ph_show_menu System
Open a shell (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
